This Application will allow you to quickly know how your Rackspace Servers are doing (among some other informations).

In the future, I will Add the ability to add/edit/delete servers, but also flavors, images and maybe more.

Checkout the github repo at https://github.com/frifri/Rackspace-manager for the latest version.

